  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5684771/" class="title-link">记住历史，重温战争的残酷，珍惜当下</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5684771"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/59647464/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59647464/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">赫赫有名</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-05"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-05 10:13:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5684771_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         最精准的战时地形图、最壮观的双方阵列图、最真实的场景还原图、最能见证历史的战场遗迹图等167幅珍贵图片，再现史上最激烈的巅峰对决时刻！      战争一旦爆发，无论规模大小，都必定是一场灾难。。。。。。     重温战争的残酷与不义，珍惜当下的幸福。。。。。。  

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5684771/#comments">(1回应)</a>
